Company Overview of Parnassus Investments



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Parnassus Investments is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to investment companies. It also caters to profit and pension sharing plans, insurance companies, foundations, endowments, corporate retirement plans, investment consultants, intermediaries, registered investment advisers, and family offices. The firm launches and manages equity and fixed income mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. The firm uses a fundamental analysis to make its investment. It conducts in-house research to make its investments. The firm does not invest in companies which indulge in manufacture of alco...
Parnassus Investments is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to investment companies. It also caters to profit and pension sharing plans, insurance companies, foundations, endowments, corporate retirement plans, investment consultants, intermediaries, registered investment advisers, and family offices. The firm launches and manages equity and fixed income mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. The firm uses a fundamental analysis to make its investment. It conducts in-house research to make its investments. The firm does not invest in companies which indulge in manufacture of alcohol or tobacco products, involved with gambling, manufacturing weapons, or generating electricity from nuclear power. It typically makes socially responsible investments. Parnassus Investments was founded in 1984 and is based in San Francisco, California.
Detailed Description


